  "story_summary": "The Bonegnawer gnolls claimed an ancient halfling barrow as their den, unaware of a dormant Void idol buried deep within. When Kael’vros the Awakener arrived to study the tomb’s necromantic secrets, his rituals shattered the runes that kept the dead at rest. Now the undead rise, the gnolls panic, and the Moribund Order seeks control. Adventurers can exploit the chaos to claim rare loot and uncover the Moribund conspiracy."
